</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     HOW IT WORKS
═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="how" id="how">
  <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="hero-badge" style="display:inline-flex;margin-bottom:24px"><span class="badge-dot"></span> HOW IT WORKS</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">From job post to hire in four steps.</h2>
    <div class="how-steps">
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="how-step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Generate Job Description</h3>
        <p>Input role details, responsibilities, and skills. Our AI builds a bias-free JD with scoring criteria in seconds.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="how-step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Invite Candidates</h3>
        <p>Share an interview link from AnytimeHire or your ATS. Candidates get interviewed autonomously, 24/7. Automatically. Both in-house and in teams.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="how-step-num">03</div>
        <h3>AI Conducts Interviews</h3>
        <p>Our AI avatar interviews hundreds of candidates simultaneously for 24/7. Realistic, in-human. Behaviours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-step">
        <div class="how-step-num">04</div>
        <h3>Review &amp; Decide</h3>
        <p>Get a ranked shortlist with scorecards, Al analysis, and recordings for each candidate. Pick the best. Done.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

