<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════
     FAQ
═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="faq" id="faq">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center">Frequently asked questions.</h2>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How does the AI avatar conduct interviews?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Our AI avatar uses a combination of natural language processing and computer vision to conduct real-time structured interviews. Candidates see and hear a realistic avatar that asks tailored questions, listens to responses, and probes deeper — just like a skilled human interviewer.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How does the scoring system work?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Every candidate response is evaluated across 4 dimensions: communication clarity, technical depth, culture fit, and problem-solving ability. Scores are generated by our proprietary AI model and presented with reasoning so hiring managers can audit every decision.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Is the AI biased?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">We go to significant lengths to remove bias. Our models are audited quarterly by a third-party ethics board. We test for demographic parity across gender, age, and ethnicity, and we publish our bias audit reports publicly.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">What do you integrate with?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">AnytimeHire integrates natively with Greenhouse, Lever, Workday, BambooHR, and 20+ other ATS platforms via our open API. We also support Zapier and webhooks for custom workflows.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">Is my data secure?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">Yes. AnytimeHire is SOC 2 Type II certified, GDPR compliant, and DPDP ready. All interview recordings and candidate data are encrypted at rest and in transit. You can configure data retention policies and request deletion at any time.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q">How fast to get started?</button>
        <div class="faq-a">You can post your first role and start interviewing candidates within 60 seconds of signing up. No setup calls, no onboarding sessions — just connect your ATS or paste a share link and go.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

